---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 108
By: Ibn 'Atâ'illâh
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Phantom Flux of Life
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Consummation of Desire
---
If thou desirest a glory that never vanishes, then seek not to embrace a
glory that vanishes.
